{"tid":1385927,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔣麗芸：阻礙列車行駛的罰則太輕　應提高罰則","createTime":"2019-07-30T08:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T08:32:55.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"690306befce8f7443593b719b0665a8ce8961732","tid":1385927,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:04:51.000Z","msg":"有網民今早在港鐵發起不合作運動，期間阻礙車門關上，又按動列車緊急掣及月台安全掣逾百次，列車嚴重受阻。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民建聯立法會議員蔣麗芸譴責這些非理性行為，已去信運輸及房屋局局長陳帆，建議參考其他交通工具法例後，考慮是否提高罰則，以起阻嚇作用。</span><br />\n<br />\n蔣麗芸認為，現時《香港鐵路附例》就有關阻礙列車行駛的罰則太輕，難起阻嚇作用，建議運房局參考其他交通工具有關阻礙車門法例後，考慮是否修改現行《香港鐵路附例》，將港鐵與其他公共交通工具看齊，加重罰則，嚴懲惡意破壞港鐵運作的乘客。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2204133/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2204133%2F&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI1IIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=f8ef4dad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2204133/</a>"},{"pid":"b93968f6e34eca4ddb317d6ab60a5908dc765c76","tid":1385927,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:06:43.000Z","msg":"Ann姐好叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9920cb3f3e6ae69103c94c326f205f582d852b84","tid":1385927,"uid":210031,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:07:32.000Z","msg":"佢呢期成日炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c5b3b87b9434169c22820ed7a77a844177cc5d","tid":1385927,"uid":73276,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:08:24.000Z","msg":"最好唔投民建聯既全部槍決添<br />\n收皮啦元秋"},{"pid":"83ecbf95f69bb6a1e0fc7592f3a13dc732e8ad59","tid":1385927,"uid":28849,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50b509796c25a3f